title: #404 - Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt with Susanna Lee
description:
Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt talk about Joey's upcoming move, making decisions, and the process you go through in life. Susanna Lee, Comedian and exotic performer, joins Joey and Lee in studio.
